GDPR gives individuals 8 type of personal data rights, please choose which right that you want to exercise in this request. 

Your right to get copies of your data

You have the right to find out if we are using or storing your personal data.

Your right to get your data corrected

You can challenge the accuracy of personal data held about you by us.

Your right to get your data deleted

You can ask us to delete personal data that we hold about you. 

Your right to limit how organisations use your data

You can limit the way we uses your personal data.

Your right to data portability

You have the right to get your personal data from us in a way that is accessible and portable . 

The right to object to the use of your data

You have the right to object us to process or use your personal data in some circumstances.

Your rights relating to decisions being made about you without human involvement

If decisions are made about you when your personal data is processed automatically. In many circumstances, you have a right to prevent automated processing.

Your right to raise a concern

Tell us if you're concerned about how we are using your data.

GDPR gives individuals 8 type of personal data rights, please choose which right that you want to exercise in this request. 

Your right to get copies of your data

You have the right to find out if we are using or storing your personal data.

Your right to get your data corrected

You can challenge the accuracy of personal data held about you by us.

Your right to get your data deleted

You can ask us to delete personal data that we hold about you. 

Your right to limit how organisations use your data

You can limit the way we uses your personal data.

Your right to data portability

You have the right to get your personal data from us in a way that is accessible and portable . 

The right to object to the use of your data

You have the right to object us to process or use your personal data in some circumstances.

Your rights relating to decisions being made about you without human involvement

If decisions are made about you when your personal data is processed automatically. In many circumstances, you have a right to prevent automated processing.

Your right to raise a concern

Tell us if you're concerned about how we are using your data.
